@startuml
title Viaverse Chat / Messaging — Sequence Diagram

actor Sender
participant "Sender Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway / App BFF" as BFF
participant "messaging-service" as Messaging
participant "marketplace-service" as Marketplace
participant "Safety Policy" as Safety
participant "media-service" as Media
database "PostgreSQL / Cassandra" as DB
participant "notification-service" as Notification

Sender -> Client : compose message
Client -> BFF : POST /conversations/{id}/messages
BFF -> Messaging : sendMessage(command)
Messaging -> Marketplace : validate quote/job context
Marketplace --> Messaging : context + allowed policy state
Messaging -> Safety : scan text + policy state
Safety --> Messaging : allow / warn / block / risk signal
Messaging -> Media : attach media refs optional
Messaging -> DB : persist message + participant state
Messaging -> DB : append read model / inbox row
Messaging -> Notification : NotificationCreated
Notification --> Client : recipient push/in-app update

Sender -> Client : open/read
Client -> BFF : POST /messages/{id}/read
BFF -> Messaging : markRead
Messaging -> DB : update read receipt

note bottom
Message send validates participant + quote/job context,
then safety policy, then persistence and notification.
Media is attached by reference.
end note
@enduml
